    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 secs, then pour in the <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Cook for 5-7 min or until reduced to a pasta sauce-like consistency</p><p>Remove from the heat and stir through a generous knob of <strong>butter </strong>with <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> chopped chives </strong>and a good grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
